加明白公司的很多工作安排为什么是那样的，更好地理解有助于你在组织中更好地、安心地工作，也更利于你为组织贡献，并获得它成功的回报。一起实践起来吧","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":169424,"uid":"1263077","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1578388259,"user_name_real":"susie"}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"66002863554","product_id":100044301,"comment_content":"我一个搬砖的开发人员居然也冲进来了，看来是膨胀了😅","like_count":15,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1263077,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/45/e5/ed4444ee.jpg","nickname":"susie","note":"","ucode":"A384ACCBCFABF2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":480551,"discussion_content":"哈哈，不膨胀，对于现在的开发人员来讲，不能只撸代码，敏捷会帮助你更好地撸代码，如果你的组织导入敏捷，你也会更加明白公司的很多工作安排为什么是那样的，更好地理解有助于你在组织中更好地、安心地工作，也更利于你为组织贡献，并获得它成功的回报。一起实践起来吧","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1578388259,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1661704,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/5b/08/b0b0db05.jpg","nickname":"丁丁历险记","note":"","ucode":"A43829E454C067","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":348735,"discussion_content":"不了解产品的套路，怎能做到知已知彼。\n不然产品是个大忽悠，你又说不出来他忽悠，那还不被人各种吊打。。。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1612695167,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":169389,"user_name":"escray","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1020525,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1F4204930E47C4","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/92/6d/becd841a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1578325697,"is_pvip":true,"replies":[{"id":"65771","content":"敏捷确实内容很多，所以先从基本的入手，了解本质，然后再往上叠加方法就容易理解了。针对开发人员，可以先学习咱们的课程，之后可以拓展到TDD等，也可以去了解DevOps的一系列实践，都是非常好的。只要勤勉，能学到的东西很多，加油！！！","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":169389,"uid":"1263077","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1578389040,"user_name_real":"susie"}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":1,"score":"27348129473","product_id":100044301,"comment_content":"其实很早就知道敏捷的概念，也看过一些关于敏捷的书，心向往之，但是却一直没有办法让敏捷落地。<br><br>敏捷现在似乎是一个相对模糊的概念，里面打包了很多具体的方法，就像留言里面提到的，用户故事、快速迭代、拥抱变化、持续交付、结对开发、测试驱动……那么敏捷的核心方法是什么？有应该从哪里开始？<br><br>我觉的敏捷主要的有点在于能够更好的实现用户的价值，同时提高程序员的效率，但是就自己的体会来说，其实对开发人员的要求也是比较高的，这大概也是我自己为什么一直不够敏捷的原因。<br><br>在开篇词里面看到说会有真实的案例，我对这个还是比较感兴趣的，另外就是其实还是想知道，从开发人员的视角，如何实现敏捷。<br><br>其实敏捷概念的引入已经很长时间了，这次是真的成为趋势，要普及了么？","like_count":6,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1263077,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/45/e5/ed4444ee.jpg","nickname":"susie","note":"","ucode":"A384ACCBCFABF2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":480536,"discussion_content":"敏捷确实内容很多，所以先从基本的入手，了解本质，然后再往上叠加方法就容易理解了。针对开发人员，可以先学习咱们的课程，之后可以拓展到TDD等，也可以去了解DevOps的一系列实践，都是非常好的。只要勤勉，能学到的东西很多，加油！！！","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1578389040,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":169277,"user_name":"Twinkle","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1340563,"ip_address":"","ucode":"FE1596741E257B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/74/93/c21f1531.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1578304038,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"65768","content":"<br><br>在敏捷中，团队成员的思想转变确实是重要的，虽然这不是敏捷的全部，却是非常重要的基础。试想一下，哪一个变革不需要做思想转变呢？都是需要的，只是个怎么转变的问题<br><br>","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":169277,"uid":"1263077","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1578388624,"user_name_real":"susie"}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"23053140518","product_id":100044301,"comment_content":"敏捷更多是整个团队每一个的思想的转变<br>","like_count":5,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1263077,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/45/e5/ed4444ee.jpg","nickname":"susie","note":"","ucode":"A384ACCBCFABF2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":480489,"discussion_content":"\n\n在敏捷中，团队成员的思想转变确实是重要的，虽然这不是敏捷的全部，却是非常重要的基础。试想一下，哪一个变革不需要做思想转变呢？都是需要的，只是个怎么转变的问题\n\n","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1578388624,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":225871,"user_name":"CJJ","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1194060,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7E02A6A8547559","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/38/4c/5426e2e0.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1591879414,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"14476781302","product_id":100044301,"comment_content":"现在好像更加流行Devops，很多网上都说Devops是敏捷开发的升级版，是真的这样吗？","like_count":3,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1492796,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/c7/3c/4802ed9f.jpg","nickname":"Felix","note":"","ucode":"E233D3F67E7814","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":549739,"discussion_content":"devops目前很流行，不过一般都是大厂，金融行业用的比较广","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden